entry.title: Ukrainian Rescuers Search for Survivors After Mall Attack
entry.content: Search efforts continued in Kremenchuk, Ukraine, the day after it was struck by Russian missiles, as Western leaders vowed fresh measures to increase economic pressure on Moscow to call off its forces.
